So it's going to be a small
number of videos this week but

57
00:03:18.290 --> 00:03:20.070
the videos are going to be fairly long,

58
00:03:20.070 --> 00:03:24.310
15 to 20 minutes, because I want to
try to introduce the tools.

59
00:03:24.310 --> 00:03:27.230
And do the cases within the same video.

60
00:03:27.230 --> 00:03:30.580
So make sure you block out plenty
of time to watch the videos,

61
00:03:30.580 --> 00:03:33.170
make sure you have enough to eat and
drink.

62
